{"tid":1808376,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（求FC）捐贈/求助生於亂世2:0嘅人唔該入來","createTime":"2020-01-02T10:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T16:19:28.000Z","uid":71995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e4921221a372bc6985f184336f371ec048b38b0","tid":1808376,"uid":71995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:26:14.000Z","msg":"（代post）<br />\n（感激朋友信任，借岀account）<br />\n<br />\n雙方各執一詞，唔易判斷件事的經過<br />\n拋磚引玉，希望知情的巴絲可以講兩句<br />\n<br />\n事源生於亂世2:0尋日開了一個post，指出有1個FB用户 See Liu抹黑他們。See Liu指遇到一位女手足，簡稱糯米飯（因為她中意食糯米飯），向生於亂世求助時遇上以下經歷（詳情可睇下面cap圖）：<br />\n1.向生於亂世求助9天後才得到食券等援助<br />\n2.接連收到2部有問題的iPhone<br />\n-iPhone 6s：無得set靜音<br />\n-iPhone 7+：home制壞，後鏡頭爆咗（及後有自稱捐贈者於生於亂世個post度留言指個後鏡頭係有1條裂痕，但不影響使用）<br />\n3.邀請糯米飯岀席party，但無通知她party改期<br />\n<br />\n作為旁觀者，見到有呢d爭議，見到支援者和求助人雙方失去信任，真係覺得惋惜。<br />\n<br />\n因為呢場運動而食人血饅頭的事實在太多（例如國難五金有老鼠貝貝、荃灣串燒保老闆娘謊稱患癌收捐款等）所以好想知呢單爭議係個別事件？有冇其他糯米飯妹妹般的經歷？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V7szM4p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV7szM4p.png&h=767002b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysnDuhK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysnDuhK.png&h=4ffa8629&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eniWfXL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeniWfXL.png&h=5b7755a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3zZqTKr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3zZqTKr.png&h=9492d550&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xOxoFpr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxOxoFpr.png&h=07f0e200&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8UGwPhN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8UGwPhN.png&h=55530e02&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qSvYuhO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqSvYuhO.png&h=24e1cfde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FLMEdKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLMEdKu.png&h=dfc78d46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDyjdKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDyjdKu.png&h=35f5e3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9yUVwwa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9yUVwwa.png&h=b807dbfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNKeM4E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNKeM4E.png&h=d609ea42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做家長的，希望大家諗清楚，自己捐贈的資源係咪真係幫助到手足。"},{"pid":"8aea0217543a35af46078e21fb581376f4d0d4d6","tid":1808376,"uid":71995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:27:19.000Z","msg":"（呢part都係代朋友岀）<br />\n另外，關於捐手機方面，我要鞭果位自稱捐iPhone 7+嘅人：<br />\n<br />\n我想問下，一部現代智能手機嘅基本功能，只係打電話，覆wtsapp，telegram?<br />\n一部可以影相、拍片嘅手機，係唔係可以用來報哨？係唔係可以做全民記者，身邊一有突發事就可以拍片？<br />\n<br />\n當然，你可以同意「一部手機鏡頭裂咗，唔影響正常操作」。咁你都可以同意用呢部機影嘅相，拍嘅片，係無問題嘅。<br />\n<br />\n己所不欲勿施於人，做人有啲同理心，唔好咁離地啦。<br />\n<br />\n捐岀1部有問題的電話仲係度自我感覺良好，你影衰哂其他盡心盡力幫手足嘅家長啊。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 無法靜音的iPhone 6S都係有問題，萬一手足走緊/避緊，附近有狗，個手機一響，手足真係多得你唔少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fZ2765k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfZ2765k.png&h=1a601405&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ba6175456b228065e719be9ce85e3a3a62231ae","tid":1808376,"uid":236894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:41:54.000Z","msg":"我之前有搵過佢哋求助<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後交收前一日 佢哋del咗我<br />\n我搵都搵唔到佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b41712f071581e987c8dfabd3c43a701d0f328","tid":1808376,"uid":300509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi